{
  "texts": [
    "Most FHE libraries lack a systematic process to select parameters for a desired application.",
    "However, external tools have been developed to help with this task for some of the most popular libraries.",
    "Table 5.9 lists some of the available open-source FHE libraries and the schemes they support.",
    "In this section, we will overview parameter selection approaches in some of the major FHE libraries and compilers.",
    "OpenFHE [BBB + 22] supports the schemes BFV, BGV, CGGI, CKKS and DM."
  ]
}